{
  "total_duration": 636.888,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 13.68,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "你有没有想过，一个随手写下的小纸条，漂了十个月以后，竟然变成一段真正的友谊？今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "A glass envelope"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“玻璃信封”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 14.03,
      "end": 26.99,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这课不是在鼓励大家把瓶子扔进海里。今天我们有环保意识，玻璃瓶进海里是不合适的。这里的瓶子是一个旧故事里的想象装置，就像一个透明的、漂在海上的信封。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 27.34,
      "end": 43.267,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先补一点地理。课文里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Holland"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，在这里指欧洲的荷兰，也就是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the Netherlands"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the Channel"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "指英吉利海峡，是英国和欧洲大陆之间的一片海。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 43.617,
      "end": 56.777,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Jane 一家横渡海峡时，她把姓名和地址写在纸上，塞进瓶子里，再把瓶子扔进海里。十个月后，瓶子带来一封来自荷兰同龄女孩的回信。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 57.127,
      "end": 69.903,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以今天的故事链是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "random message, surprise reply, same-age friend, regular letters, reliable post office"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。瓶子带来惊喜，邮局让联系真正稳定下来。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 70.253,
      "end": 81.557,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一帧，我们先看一张很简单、没有文字标签的方位图。左边是英国，右边是欧洲大陆，中间这条海就是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the Channel"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 81.906,
      "end": 94.074,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "地图不用背，只要明白路线：Jane 是在横渡英吉利海峡时放下瓶子的，瓶子后来漂向荷兰，也就是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the Netherlands"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的方向。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 94.424,
      "end": 103.664,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一步很重要。没有这张小地图，孩子可能只听到“瓶子漂到了 Holland”，却不知道它大概从哪里到哪里。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 104.014,
      "end": 110.254,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二帧，Jane 在船上。她把自己的名字和地址写在一张纸上。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 110.604,
      "end": 123.087,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Jane put a piece of paper with her name and address on it into a bottle."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "address"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是能收到信的地址。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "into a bottle"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是放进瓶子里。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 123.437,
      "end": 139.249,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "接着："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "She threw the bottle into the sea."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "threw"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "throw"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的过去式，意思是扔、投。这里要理解成旧故事里的浪漫偶然，不是今天要模仿的行为。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 139.599,
      "end": 149.479,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三帧，Jane 完全忘了这件事。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "She never thought of it again."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "她再也没有想起那个瓶子。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 149.828,
      "end": 158.06,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "但十个月以后，惊喜来了："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "she received a letter from a girl in Holland"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。这个女孩和 Jane 差不多大。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 158.41,
      "end": 175.27,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "开头那句也在这里回来了："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Jane never dreamed of receiving a letter from a girl of her own age in Holland."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "never dreamed of receiving"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是从没想过会收到；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a girl of her own age"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是和她同龄的女孩。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 175.62,
      "end": 183.78,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四帧，故事从偶然变成稳定联系。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Both girls write to each other regularly now."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 184.129,
      "end": 195.897,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "write to each other"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是互相写信，不是只有一个人写。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "regularly"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是有规律地、一次又一次地，不只是那一封神奇的回信。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 196.247,
      "end": 211.911,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后她们做了一个很实际的决定："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "they have decided to use the post office"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。邮局寄信会"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "cost a little more"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，稍微多花一点钱，但信会"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "travel faster"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，到得更快。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 212.26,
      "end": 222.38,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这就是标题的妙处。瓶子像一个玻璃信封，帮她们第一次遇见；但真正让友谊继续下去的，是更可靠的邮局。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 222.73,
      "end": 232.33,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这课最容易误会四个地方："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Holland"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the Channel"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、瓶中信，还有为什么结尾突然改用邮局。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 232.68,
      "end": 235.455,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Holland"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是哪里？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 235.805,
      "end": 247.389,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这篇课文里，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Holland"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "指荷兰，也就是现在常说的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the Netherlands"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。简单记：它在欧洲大陆靠海的一边。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 247.738,
      "end": 250.912,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the Channel"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "又是什么？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 251.262,
      "end": 264.142,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the English Channel"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，英吉利海峡。它在英国和欧洲大陆之间。Jane 横渡这片海时，瓶子才有了漂向欧洲大陆的故事路线。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 264.492,
      "end": 267.679,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那我可以也写个纸条扔进海里吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 268.029,
      "end": 280.509,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不可以。今天我们知道这会污染海洋，也可能伤到环境。课文里的瓶子要当作旧故事里的想象装置来理解，就像童话里的道具，不是现实生活建议。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 280.859,
      "end": 284.501,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么题目叫"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "A glass envelope"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 284.85,
      "end": 293.61,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为瓶子像一个透明的信封，里面装着纸条和地址。它很神奇，但很慢，也很不可靠。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 293.96,
      "end": 296.923,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那为什么最后要用邮局？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 297.273,
      "end": 305.353,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为友谊不该一直靠运气。瓶子制造了第一次惊喜，但邮局能让她们更稳定、更快地互相写信。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 305.703,
      "end": 311.127,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "My daughter, Jane, never dreamed of receiving a letter from a girl of her own age in Holland."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 311.477,
      "end": 318.197,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Last year, we were travelling across the Channel and Jane put a piece of paper with her name and address on it into a bottle."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 318.547,
      "end": 321.331,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "She threw the bottle into the sea."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 321.681,
      "end": 327.273,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "She never thought of it again, but ten months later, she received a letter from a girl in Holland."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 327.623,
      "end": 330.959,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Both girls write to each other regularly now."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 331.309,
      "end": 335.005,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "However, they have decided to use the post office."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 35,
      "start": 335.354,
      "end": 339.986,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Letters will cost a little more, but they will certainly travel faster."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 36,
      "start": 340.336,
      "end": 342.904,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "dream"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "dream"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 37,
      "start": 343.254,
      "end": 344.814,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "dream"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "dream"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 38,
      "start": 345.164,
      "end": 356.692,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "dream"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "dream"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可以是做梦，也可以表示想象、料到。课文里的重点是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "never dreamed of receiving"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，从没想过会收到。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 39,
      "start": 357.042,
      "end": 366.234,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "dream"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Jane never dreamed of receiving a letter."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是说她睡觉梦见信，而是说她完全没料到会收到这样一封信。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 40,
      "start": 366.583,
      "end": 377.931,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "dream"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这个结构后面常接"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "-ing"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "形式："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "dreamed of receiving"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，想象收到；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "dreamed of meeting"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，想象遇见。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 41,
      "start": 378.281,
      "end": 380.865,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "Channel"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Channel"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 42,
      "start": 381.215,
      "end": 382.823,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "Channel"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Channel"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 43,
      "start": 383.172,
      "end": 394.28,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "Channel"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Channel"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "本来可以表示水道、海峡。在这篇课文里，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the Channel"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "指"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the English Channel"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，英吉利海峡。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 44,
      "start": 394.63,
      "end": 401.946,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "Channel"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "we were travelling across the Channel"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，意思是我们正在横渡英吉利海峡。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 45,
      "start": 402.296,
      "end": 410.656,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "Channel"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这不是让你背欧洲地图，只是帮你看懂：英国在一边，欧洲大陆在另一边，瓶子才有可能漂向荷兰方向。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 46,
      "start": 411.006,
      "end": 414.021,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "regularly"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "regularly"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 47,
      "start": 414.371,
      "end": 416.219,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "regularly"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "regularly"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 48,
      "start": 416.569,
      "end": 424.745,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "regularly"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "regularly"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的意思是有规律地、经常地、稳定地反复发生。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 49,
      "start": 425.095,
      "end": 433.975,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "regularly"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Both girls write to each other regularly now."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这说明她们不是只联系了一次，而是后来固定写信。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 50,
      "start": 434.325,
      "end": 446.56,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "regularly"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "你也可以说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I practise English regularly."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "或者"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "We meet regularly after school."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "重点是“不是偶然一次，而是持续发生”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 51,
      "start": 446.91,
      "end": 454.342,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "grammar"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不从复杂时态开始，而是抓几组“人与人建立联系”的表达。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 52,
      "start": 454.692,
      "end": 468.551,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一组："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "of her own age"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。课文里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a girl of her own age"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，就是和 Jane 差不多大的女孩。你可以说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a boy of my own age"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，和我同龄的男孩。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 53,
      "start": 468.901,
      "end": 481.381,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二组："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "write to each other"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "each other"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是互相、彼此。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "They write to each other"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是两个人互相写信，不是单向联系。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 54,
      "start": 481.731,
      "end": 491.986,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三组："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "regularly"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。它把一次偶然回复变成长期通信："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "They write to each other regularly."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 55,
      "start": 492.336,
      "end": 506.924,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四组："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a little more, but faster"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Letters will cost a little more, but they will certainly travel faster."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这是一个实用比较：多花一点点钱，换来更快、更可靠。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 56,
      "start": 507.274,
      "end": 520.114,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以这一课真正有用的表达是：同龄人、互相联系、持续联系、选择更可靠的方式。瓶子制造偶然，语言帮我们说清楚关系怎样继续。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 57,
      "start": 520.464,
      "end": 536.504,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "现在把今天的故事放进自己的生活。不要写“我要把瓶子扔进海里”，而是写一个安全、被家长或老师知道的偶然连接：夏令营朋友、班级交换、亲戚介绍的笔友，或者一次学校活动认识的同龄人。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 58,
      "start": 536.854,
      "end": 545.894,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的小框架是：先说你没想到会收到谁的消息，再说对方和你差不多大，然后说明你们现在怎样稳定联系。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 59,
      "start": 546.244,
      "end": 560.599,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "比如："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I never dreamed of receiving a message from a camp friend. She is of my own age. Now we write to each other regularly. Email is free, but a postcard feels more special."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 60,
      "start": 560.949,
      "end": 568.885,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "也可以用现代版本："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "We first met by chance, but now we use messages because they are faster and more reliable."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 61,
      "start": 569.235,
      "end": 582.611,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "下面练习里，用"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "word bank"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "填空，说清楚：你们怎么偶然认识，为什么是同龄人，现在怎样稳定联系，以及你为什么选择那个联系方式。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 62,
      "start": 582.961,
      "end": 604.404,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "outro",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一课就到这。下面先做 ⓪ 跟读：听课文全文 -> 听原音 -> 录一句 -> 获取反馈，把"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "never dreamed of receiving"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "of her own age"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "across the Channel"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "write to each other regularly"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "和"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "travel faster"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "读顺。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 63,
      "start": 604.754,
      "end": 620.794,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "outro",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "跟读之后，再做 ① 生活场景，用英语说一个偶然认识、后来稳定联系的朋友；后面 ② 完形 ③ 中译英 ④ 英译中 ⑤ 默写 一条线做下来。做完以后，爸爸的邮箱里就会收到你今天的成绩。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 64,
      "start": 621.144,
      "end": 636.888,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "outro",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "记住今天的结尾：瓶子像一个"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "glass envelope"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，带来了第一次惊喜；但真正可靠的通信，还是要靠更稳定的方式。The bottle begins the friendship, but the post office keeps it going."
        }
      ]
    }
